<h2>Sit.  Tweet.  Reflect.</h2>

<p>One Cushion is a simple support tool for people who choose to spend time in meditation.  We ride on top of Twitter to make it easy.</p>

<h2>How do I get started?</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Perform your meditation.</li>
  <li>Send a tweet that includes the time you spent meditating and the #onecushion hashtag.</li>	
  <li>Watch it appear here.</li>
</ol>

<p>Want to know more?  Check out our <a href="http://onecushion.tumblr.com">blog</a>.</p>

<%if @tweets%>
<h2>Take a look at the latest updates:</h2>
<ul style="padding:0;">
<%@tweets.each do |t|%>
	<li style="margin: 5px; padding: 0; list-style:none;">
		<div style="float: left; width: 60px; margin:0; padding:0;">
			<img style="margin-top:5px; padding:0;" src="<%=t.profile_image_url%>" />
		</div>
		<div style="float: left; width: 650px; margin:0; padding:0;">
			
				<p style="padding:0; margin:0;"><a href="http://twitter.com/<%=t.from_user%>"><%=t.from_user%></a> <%=t.text.to_html%></p>
			
		</div>
		<div style="clear:both;">&nbsp;</div>
	</li>
<%end%>
</ul>
<%end%>